   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Account of sowing barley: Hathyr 30 of the 20th year  for sowing barley, 1 art., 2 metra; &lt;Choiak&gt; 1, likewise another 1 art., 6 metra; 3, another 1 1/2  art.; 7, another 1 art. 6 metra; 8, another 1 art. 2 metra; 9, likewise 1 art. 2 metra; . . ., likewise in all 1 art., 1/2 metron; and for (preparation of) malt, 1/2 art.; Tybi 1, to Sarapion, 1 metron; 5, to Sarapion . . ."</ab>
